        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-27 20:30:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@Jessica:\nHi Jess, I was busy testing a similar patch and verified the tox sonar fix for pmsh. Just hope it doesn't break the other builds.\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/ci-management/+/102525/\n\nSeems to push the results to SonarCloud correctly.\nhttps://sonarcloud.io/dashboard?id=onap_dcaegen2-services-pmsh\n\nThe WhiteSource job seems ok too.\nhttps://saas.whitesourcesoftware.com/Wss/WSS.html#!project;id=1992604\n\nI can add the SonarCloud conf to the platform-submodule too if it's easier.\n\nFiach",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "3fde29e81488a0467a26b98677666df1cbda2878",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4405,
