          "email": "fiachra.corcoran@est.tech",
          "username": "efiacor"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-27 20:41:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> @Jessica:\n > Hi Jess, I was busy testing a similar patch and verified the tox\n > sonar fix for pmsh. Just hope it doesn't break the other builds.\n > \n > https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/ci-management/+/102525/\n > \n > Seems to push the results to SonarCloud correctly.\n > https://sonarcloud.io/dashboard?id=onap_dcaegen2-services-pmsh\n > \n > The WhiteSource job seems ok too.\n > https://saas.whitesourcesoftware.com/Wss/WSS.html#!project;id=1992604\n > \n > I can add the SonarCloud conf to the platform-submodule too if it's\n > easier.\n > \n > Fiach\n\nPS. I reverted to using the ubuntu node but tested in SandBox using the centos node. Not sure if this is a concern.",
        "patchset_number": 1
